zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2534525\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2534525\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104znp1665702699570.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/znp1665702699570.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/znp1665702699570.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"znp1665702699570\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     \n $storetype \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"znp1665702699570___storetype_290511\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the type of update for the current occurrence.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"znp1665702699570__topic_d89732e1_d89733e1_d89734e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"znp1665702699570__p_d89735e1_d89736e1_d89737e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$storetype</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"znp1665702699570__section_w1557ab1b7b5_w1558ab1b7_w1559ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"znp1665702699570__p_d89738e1_d89739e1_d89740e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">if ($storetype = 1)</code> ...</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"znp1665702699570__topic_d59697e1_d59698e1_d59699e1_d59700e1_d59701e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1206638e84\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"znp1665702699570__d6157e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"znp1665702699570__d6157e20__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"znp1665702699570__d6157e20__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"znp1665702699570__d6157e20__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"znp1665702699570__d6157e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"znp1665702699570__d6157e20__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"znp1665702699570__d6157e20__entry__3\">\n Entity name. If omitted, the current entity is used.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"znp1665702699570__topic_d59702e1_d59703e1_d59704e1_d59705e1_d59706e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1206638e138\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"znp1665702699570__p_d89747e1_d89748e1_d89749e1\">Returns a Boolean value or empty string prior to the execution of the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">write</span> statement in the write trigger:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9710e1_d9711e1_d9712e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$storetype</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9710e1_d9711e1_d9712e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value \n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9710e1_d9711e1_d9712e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9710e1_d9711e1_d9712e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9710e1_d9711e1_d9712e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n The occurrence will be inserted in the database.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9710e1_d9711e1_d9712e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9710e1_d9711e1_d9712e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n The occurrence will be updated in the database.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9710e1_d9711e1_d9712e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n \"\"\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9710e1_d9711e1_d9712e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n An error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9713e1_d9714e1_d9715e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$storetype</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9713e1_d9714e1_d9715e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9713e1_d9714e1_d9715e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Error constant</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9713e1_d9714e1_d9715e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Meaning</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9713e1_d9714e1_d9715e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">-1102</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9713e1_d9714e1_d9715e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">&lt;UPROCERR_ENTITY&gt;</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9713e1_d9714e1_d9715e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not included in the component structure.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"znp1665702699570__topic_d59707e1_d59708e1_d59709e1_d59710e1_d59711e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1206638e281\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"znp1665702699570__p_d89753e1_d89754e1_d89755e1\">Allowed in all component types, but only in the write trigger.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"znp1665702699570__topic_d59712e1_d59713e1_d59714e1_d59715e1_d59716e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1206638e290\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"znp1665702699570__p_d89759e1_d89760e1_d89761e1\">The function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$storetype</span> indicates the type of update of the current occurrence in the specified entity. Events that affect the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$storetype</span> are shown in the following table:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9716e1_d9717e1_d9718e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 4. </span><span class=\"title\">Statements that change <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$storetype</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9716e1_d9717e1_d9718e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Event</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9716e1_d9717e1_d9718e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Action</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9716e1_d9717e1_d9718e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yrm1665702560304.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yrm1665702560304.html\" title=\"Creates an empty occurrence of the specified entity.\">creocc</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9716e1_d9717e1_d9718e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Sets <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$storetype</span> to 1.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9716e1_d9717e1_d9718e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vxw1719821718668.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vxw1719821718668.html\" title=\"Release database controls.\">release</a>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">/mod</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9716e1_d9717e1_d9718e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Sets <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$storetype</span> to 1.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9716e1_d9717e1_d9718e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cyd1665702599286.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cyd1665702599286.html\" title=\"Activate the read trigger for the first outermost entity and all related entities, or for a specific entity.\">retrieve</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9716e1_d9717e1_d9718e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Sets <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$storetype</span> to 0.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9716e1_d9717e1_d9718e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">^ADD_OCC</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"znp1665702699570__table_d9716e1_d9717e1_d9718e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Sets <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$storetype</span> to 1.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"znp1665702699570__p_d89762e1_d89763e1_d89764e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$storetype</span> is also affected by the\n            reconnect process initiated by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">reconnect</span> or\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/reconnect</span>. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qnx1665702574893.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qnx1665702574893.html#qnx1665702574893__XREF_OccModState\">Table 4</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"znp1665702699570__p_d89765e1_d89766e1_d89767e1\">The value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$storetype</span> is reset to 0 immediately following a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">write</span> statement in the write trigger.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"znp1665702699570__p_d89768e1_d89769e1_d89770e1\">(Prior to V6.1, the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$storetype</span> remained unchanged until the end of the write trigger.)</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"znp1665702699570__section_rfs_wz3_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1206638e468\">Example: Logging Modification Information About Occurrences</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example uses the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$storetype</span> function\n               in the write trigger to determine whether an occurrence is being inserted or updated.\n               If it is being updated, the occurrence already exists; if it is being inserted, the\n               occurrence must be a new one. The example logs information about which user updated\n               or created a particular occurrence.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"znp1665702699570__pre_hfg_xz3_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; trigger: Write\nif ($storetype = 1)\n putmess \"new occurrence\"\n CREATED_BY = $user\n CREATED_DATE = $date\nelse\n UPDATED_BY = $user\n putmess \"existing occurrence updated by %%$user%%%\"\nendif\nwrite\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Note that the same result can be achieved using\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$dbocc</span>.</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nht1665702561308.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>write</a><p>Write the current occurrence to the database.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534525\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534525\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$storetype Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $storetype Return the type of update for the current occurrence. $storetype { ( Entity ) } Example: if ($storetype = 1) ... Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Entity name. If omitted, the current entity is used. Return Values Returns a Boolean value or empty string prior to the execution of the write statement in the write trigger: Table 2. Values returned by $storetype Value Meaning 1 The occurrence will be inserted in the database. 0 The occurrence will be updated in the database. \"\" An error occurred. procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Table 3. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following $storetype Value Error constant Meaning -1102 <UPROCERR_ENTITY> The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not included in the component structure. Use Allowed in all component types, but only in the write trigger. Description The function $storetype indicates the type of update of the current occurrence in the specified entity. Events that affect the value of $storetype are shown in the following table: Table 4. Statements that change $storetype Event Action creocc Sets $storetype to 1. release /mod Sets $storetype to 1. retrieve Sets $storetype to 0. ^ADD_OCC Sets $storetype to 1. $storetype is also affected by the reconnect process initiated by reconnect or retrieve/reconnect . For more information, see Table 4 . The value of $storetype is reset to 0 immediately following a write statement in the write trigger. (Prior to V6.1, the value of $storetype remained unchanged until the end of the write trigger.) Example: Logging Modification Information About Occurrences The following example uses the $storetype function in the write trigger to determine whether an occurrence is being inserted or updated. If it is being updated, the occurrence already exists; if it is being inserted, the occurrence must be a new one. The example logs information about which user updated or created a particular occurrence. ; trigger: Write if ($storetype = 1) putmess \"new occurrence\" CREATED_BY = $user CREATED_DATE = $date else UPDATED_BY = $user putmess \"existing occurrence updated by %%$user%%%\" endif write Copy Note that the same result can be achieved using $dbocc . Related Links write Write the current occurrence to the database. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}